root: ^Congratulations. You live to blabber another day.
^Like I said before, she's with Doritha, further in the house.
^The home warped quite a bit when we arrived.
^The people who have lived and loved in this home.
^The lining between our world and yours thinned a few hours ago and we came like bees to honey. It was like someone was calling to us.
^With your family, working their way in. I don't know what they see in you all.
^You? Oh god no. Yasmin's got that covered.
^I'm just here to watch it all go down. Not much exciting happens on The Otherside.
^You want to save them? I don't believe you, but you can keep saying that until you've convinced yourself.
